22namespace webrtc {
23namespace vcm {
24
25int64_t VCMProcessTimer::Period() const {
26 return _periodMs;
27}
28
29int64_t VCMProcessTimer::TimeUntilProcess() const {
30 const int64_t time_since_process = _clock->TimeInMilliseconds() - _latestMs;
31 const int64_t time_until_process = _periodMs - time_since_process;
32 return std::max<int64_t>(time_until_process, 0);
33}
34
35void VCMProcessTimer::Processed() {
36 _latestMs = _clock->TimeInMilliseconds();
37}
38} // namespace vcm
39
40namespace {
41
42class VideoCodingModuleImpl : public VideoCodingModule {
43 public:
44 explicit VideoCodingModuleImpl(Clock* clock)
45 : VideoCodingModule(),
46 timing_(new VCMTiming(clock)),
47 receiver_(clock, timing_.get()) {}
48
49 ~VideoCodingModuleImpl() override {}
50
51 int64_t TimeUntilNextProcess() override {
52 int64_t receiver_time = receiver_.TimeUntilNextProcess();
53 RTC_DCHECK_GE(receiver_time, 0);
54 return receiver_time;
55 }
56
57 void Process() override { receiver_.Process(); }
58
59 int32_t RegisterReceiveCodec(uint8_t payload_type,
60 const VideoCodec* receiveCodec,
61 int32_t numberOfCores) override {
62 return receiver_.RegisterReceiveCodec(payload_type, receiveCodec,
63 numberOfCores);
64 }
65
66 void RegisterExternalDecoder(VideoDecoder* externalDecoder,
67 uint8_t payloadType) override {
68 receiver_.RegisterExternalDecoder(externalDecoder, payloadType);
69 }
70
71 int32_t RegisterReceiveCallback(
72 VCMReceiveCallback* receiveCallback) override {
73 RTC_DCHECK(construction_thread_.IsCurrent());
74 return receiver_.RegisterReceiveCallback(receiveCallback);
75 }
76
77 int32_t RegisterFrameTypeCallback(
78 VCMFrameTypeCallback* frameTypeCallback) override {
79 return receiver_.RegisterFrameTypeCallback(frameTypeCallback);
80 }
81
82 int32_t RegisterPacketRequestCallback(
83 VCMPacketRequestCallback* callback) override {
84 RTC_DCHECK(construction_thread_.IsCurrent());
85 return receiver_.RegisterPacketRequestCallback(callback);
86 }
87
88 int32_t Decode(uint16_t maxWaitTimeMs) override {
89 return receiver_.Decode(maxWaitTimeMs);
90 }
91
92 int32_t IncomingPacket(const uint8_t* incomingPayload,
93 size_t payloadLength,
94 const RTPHeader& rtp_header,
95 const RTPVideoHeader& video_header) override {
96 return receiver_.IncomingPacket(incomingPayload, payloadLength, rtp_header,
97 video_header);
98 }
99
100 void SetNackSettings(size_t max_nack_list_size,
101 int max_packet_age_to_nack,
102 int max_incomplete_time_ms) override {
103 return receiver_.SetNackSettings(max_nack_list_size, max_packet_age_to_nack,
104 max_incomplete_time_ms);
105 }
106
107 private:
108 SequenceChecker construction_thread_;
109 const std::unique_ptr<VCMTiming> timing_;
110 vcm::VideoReceiver receiver_;
111};
112} // namespace
113
114// DEPRECATED. Create method for current interface, will be removed when the
115// new jitter buffer is in place.
116VideoCodingModule* VideoCodingModule::Create(Clock* clock) {
117 RTC_DCHECK(clock);
118 return new VideoCodingModuleImpl(clock);
119}
